 D1_Situation {
  coords 1339.456 39 2158.43
  m_sTitle "I. Situation"
  m_sTextData "2 Weeks ago Soviet troops overwhelmed the Arland National Guard troops defending the island of Arland. This was an extension of the Soviet invasion of Everon to give them a buffer as the take over Everon. The troops were able to evacuate all of the civilians on the island and have since gone into hiding from the soviets. Today, US Marines will launch a coordinated amphibious invasion of the island."\
  ""\
  "A. Enemy Forces"\
  "Large amounts of Soviet Motor Rifle elements have been spotted in the AO. We expect more resistance near the coast, where more assets have been offloaded over the last week. As of last night, no special forces, armor elements, or air assets have been spotted on the island, though the soviets did use Mi-8's to help with their initial assault of the island."\
  ""\
  ""\
  ""\
  "B. Friendly Forces."\
  "You, a US Marine AH1S Apache Attack Helicopter squad are currently preparing to launch from the USS Concrete, north of the island.(Out of the Map, but just fly south)"\
  "Several Marine units have been deployed between amphibious landings and helicopter landings to operate all across the island. FACs will coordinate with you to ensure you engage the correct targets."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "US"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 D2_Mission {
  coords 1337.024 39 2138.321
  m_sTitle "II. Mission"
  m_sTextData "A. Destroy the Soviet communications center at Singal Hill."\
  "Upon launching from the USS Concrete head to Signal Hill and disrupt their communications center to prevent them from coordinating a strong defense."\
  ""\
  "B. Respond to CAS request from Marine infantry."\
  "Listen for FAC's calls for Close Air Support missions and respond as requested."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "US"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 D3_Execution {
  coords 1334.265 39 2143.766
  m_sTitle "III. Execution"
  m_sTextData "A. Concept of Operation"\
  ""\
  "Phase 1: Disable the Soviet communications center at Signal Hill"\
  "Phase 2: Respond to request by FAC until US Marines have taken a solid foothold on the island."\
  ""\
  ""\
  ""\
  "B. Maneuver"\
  "Per Commanders Intent"\
  ""\
  "Note: Pilots do not need FAC or Flight leads permission to resupply. If you are running low communicate you are going to resupply and get more ammunitions. You are not useful if you don't have armaments. DO try to coordinate with your squad to ensure there are always CAS assets available to support ground troops."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
